  "<mainText>{{Spell_SettPassive_Tooltip}}<br><br><rules>Sett will reset back to a left punch if he does not do a right punch within 2 seconds of doing a left punch. The <attackSpeed>Attack Speed</attackSpeed> of a right punch is 8 times that of a left punch.</rules></mainText>": 1,
  "<mainText>PASSIVE: Morgana's damaging attacks and abilities 50% <TFTKeyword>Shred</TFTKeyword> and <TFTKeyword>Sunder</TFTKeyword> enemies.<br><br>ACTIVE: Morgana spawns growing toxic pools under random targets for @Duration@ seconds. The pools deal @TotalDamage@ magic damage every second and heal Morgana for @OmnivampPercent*100@% of the damage dealt.<br><br><tftitemrules><tftbold>Sunder</tftbold>: reduce Armor<br><tftbold>Shred</tftbold>: reduce Magic Resist</tftitemrules>@SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@</mainText>": 10,
  "<mainText><stats><attention>%i:scaleAP% 100</attention> Ability Power<br><attention>%i:scaleHealth% 150</attention> Health<br><attention>%i:scaleCooldown% 15</attention> Ability Haste</stats>{{ Item_Passive_List }}<li><passive>Hypershot:</passive> Damaging a champion with a non-targeted Ability at over 700 range or <status>Slowing or Immobilizing</status> them <keywordStealth>Reveals</keywordStealth> them and increases their damage taken from you.<br><br><rules>The Ability that triggers <passive>Hypershot</passive> also benefits from the damage increase. Pets and non-immobilizing traps do not trigger this effect. Only the initial placement of zone Abilities will trigger this effect. Distance is measured from the Ability cast position. </rules></mainText>": 1,
